ここ ~ koko ~ here (near speaker)
そこ ~ soko ~ there (near listener)
あそこ ~ asoko ~ that over there (far from speaker and listener)
みぎ ~ migi ~ right
ひだり ~ hidari ~ left
ひがし ~ higashi ~ east
にし ~ nishi ~ west
みなみ ~ minami ~ south 
きた ~ kita ~ north
むかい ~ mukai ~ opposite, other side, across the street
となり ~ tonari ~ next to, near
まえ ~ mae ~ in front of
うしろ ~ ushiro ~ back, behind
まっすぐ ~ massugu ~ straight, direct
みち ~ michi ~ road, street, way, path, route
だいがく ~ daigaku ~ university, college
ちゅうがっこう ~ chuugakkou ~ junior high school, middle school
しょうがっこう ~ shougakkou ~ primary school, elementary school
こうとうがっこう ~ koutougakkou ~ senior high school, high school
びょういん ~ byouin ~ hospital
えき ~ eki ~ station
こうえん ~ kouen ~ park
どうぶつえん　~ doubutsuen ~ zoo
うち ~ uchi ~ house
スーパー ~ suupaa ~ super market
かわ ~ kawa ~ river
やま ~ yama ~ mountain
うみ ~ umi ~ sea
みずうみ ~ mizuumi ~ lake